modules.description: This module implements low-level network communication using rawlink interfaces as MirageOS flow devices, enabling direct packet transmission and reception. It works with `Cstruct.t` buffers and `Lwt_rawlink.t` flow handles, providing operations to read, write, and close network flows with explicit error handling. Concrete use cases include implementing custom network protocols, packet filtering, and direct Ethernet frame manipulation in unikernel-based systems.
